(3631, 4685, NULL, '1774669924_3416624192423', 1, '1774669924', 'Mojtaba Ziyadi', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, 'Ok here is the thing: Some of my fiends and many other people in Iran keep asking me "How can I come there(US)?" or "How should I apply for study or job?"... When I ask for their reason or goal they just simply reply; "I am tired of this country" "I want to leave this f* country" "I want to be happy and enjoy my life". Apparently for the last response, being far from family&friends and abandoning the parents is their "happiness"... Ok then come and "ENJOY" your life...\n\nOh man, these are not goals when you apply... I am tired of these kind of questions... you need to change your mind... Most of them are ready to pay 40-50,000 $ per semester to just to leave the country... Crazzzy...\nWhere are we going? :( ... Someone help me please... :( I am really tired of explaining why they should apply and -most of the cases- why they should not even think about it....\n\nWithin one year I can tell you more than 10 people asked me these questions (beside many others who really had goals and I know them very well and are good students and have hunger to learn)... \nNevertheless, I always try to show them (respectfully) the best way that best fits their case.', 45, '2013-09-07 14:54:08', NULL, NULL),
