(4618, 5358, NULL, '605536314_10151651575981315', 1, '605536314', 'James Falzone', NULL, 'http://momentadances.org/dances-for-autumn/', 'https://fbexternal-a.akamaihd.net/safe_image.php?d=AQAJ7KUcIruhlp_h&w=154&h=154&url=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.squarespace.com%2Fstatic%2F51645a59e4b09c821721d3fd%2Ft%2F52334e55e4b0587d98e0a497%2F%3Fformat%3D500w', NULL, 'Dances for Autumn', 'MOMENTA presents its 2013 Fall Evening Concerts. Historical Choreographers: August Bournonville, Isadora Duncan, Marius Petipa. Contemporary Choreographers: Stephanie Clemens, Sarah Cullen Fuller, Sandra Kaufmann, Anita Kenney, Cora D. Mitchell, Tom Trimble. ', 'Looking forward to a collaboration with choreographer Sarah Fuller this weekend and next with the Momenta Dance Company. Sarah has created some fantastic movement to a piece I wrote for her called Butterfly or Falling Leaf. The ensemble performing includes myself, Ellen McSweeney, Liz Weamer and Tom Holmes and the music was inspired by a poem by Philip Larkin (via Timothy Daisy)\n\n   Butterfly Or falling leaf,\n   Which ought I to imitate\n   In my dancing?\n\nAnd if she were to admit\nThe world weaved by her feet\nIs leafless, is incomplete?\nAnd if she abandoned it,\nBroke the pivoted dance,\nSet loose the audience?\nThen would the moon go raving,\nThe moon, the anchorless\nMoon go swerving\nDown at the earth for a catastrophic kiss.', 50, '2013-10-29 13:06:07', NULL, NULL),
