(4953, 5523, NULL, '1721348687_3659342298447', 1, '1721348687', 'Sam Gould', NULL, 'https://www.facebook.com/photo.php?fbid=3659342138443&set=a.2582722223618.70123.1721348687&type=1&relevant_count=1', 'https://fbcdn-photos-h-a.akamaihd.net/hphotos-ak-prn2/v/1388045_3659348738608_717061389_s.jpg?oh=328d2a8376405973ab100304350d4a18&oe=5273171E&__gda__=1383367113_0668239585837b437832e24bea8feea1', NULL, 'iOS Photos', NULL, 'More Lou: remembering me at 19 in some long ago shuttered record shop in the village trying to buy a cd and some guy comes in and asks if they have a copy of Pet Sounds. The guys behind the counter stop everything and immediately check and then lead the guy to the section. Muttering to one another in whispers  about the mystery customer as I wait to pay I say, "yes, it was fucking Lou Reed. Can I pay for my god damn record already?" Ah, to be young and yet to be filled with PacNW zen. Glad I''m not that guy anymore.', 50, '2013-10-28 10:20:01', NULL, NULL);
